snippet.textDisplay:
Being a fan of Coke Studio Pakistan I was waiting eagerly for the 10th season but was a little disappointed. This song was not up to the mark as per standards set by Coke Studio Pakistan. Music was way too loud to hear the singers. 
Read a few comments about referral of Danyal Zafar by his elder brother but I guess he has talent. Not sure why people are not  saying the same thing about Momina though she is also there due to her family's influence. Of all the artists featured in Coke Studio Pakistan she is the least deserving singer.

Hope to see better songs in future episodes.

Requesting Strings to call back Ustaad Naseeruddin Sami Sahab for a song and have Jafer Zaidi compose the music for the same.
